We loved it, comments, 'Outstanding!' Very light, compared to potato salad and so easy. I used rinsed and drained black eyed peas(2 cans), so I'm not sure it the proportions were correct. Offered the minced jalapeno at the table. Next time I want to make it by the book and double the recipe. Was great with barbequed chicken. Sadly, there were no leftovers.

